  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Environmental education to argentinean children</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project will provide environmental education through didactic workshops to 600 children from 5 to 8 years old in schools in  Argentina. Through these workshops the project will propose several activities in order to bring about such topics as the life cycle of plants and recycling and the relationship between them and the lives of children. The workshops focus its actions in promoting participation of children as agents of change in their homes in creating new habits of sustainability.</narrative>
  </description>
